<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ton Nom - Portfolio Académique</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #2c3e50; --accent: #3498db; --bg: #ffffff; --light: #f8f9fa; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; margin: 0; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        /* Menu style "Onglets" */
        nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        nav ul { display: flex; justify-content: center; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
        nav ul li a { display: block; padding: 20px 25px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; }
        nav ul li a:hover { color: var(--accent); background: var(--light); }

        /* Conteneur principal */
        .container { max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 20px 60px; }

        /* En-tête */
        header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        header img { width: 140px; height: 140px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 4px solid white; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 10px 0; color: var(--primary); }
        .tagline { font-style: italic; color: #666; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        /* Sections */
        section { padding-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        h2 { font-family: 'Lora', serif; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.6rem; }
        
        /* Listes de travaux */
        .entry { margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 15px; border-left: 3px solid #eee; transition: 0.3s; }
        .entry:hover { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
        .entry-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: block; }
        .entry-meta { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #777; font-style: italic; }
        
        /* Boutons de liens */
        .btn-group { margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 20px; margin-right: 8px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#about">Bio</a></li>
            <li><a href="#posters">Posters</a></li>
            <li><a href="#publications">Publications</a></li>
            <li><a href="#associations">Associations</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <header id="about">
            <img src="https://github.com/ERedh.png" alt="Photo de profil">
            <h1>[Ton Prénom] [Ton Nom]</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Doctorant / Chercheur / Étudiant en [Ton Domaine]</p>
            <p>Ici, tu peux écrire un petit texte sur tes recherches actuelles. Par exemple : "Mes travaux portent sur l'impact de l'IA dans l'éducation spécialisée..."</p>
        </header>

        <hr>

        <section id="posters">
            <h2>🖼 Présentations & Posters</h2>
            <div class="entry">
                <span class="entry-title">L'impact des technologies émergentes en 2026</span>
                <span class="entry-meta">Conférence Internationale de Paris, Mai 2026</span>
                <div class="btn-group">
                    <a href="#" class="btn">PDF</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">Affiche</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="publications">
            <h2>📚 Publications</h2>
            <div class="entry">
                <span class="entry-title">Analyse comparative des méthodes de recherche X et Y</span>
                <span class="entry-meta">Publié dans : Revue des Sciences Appliquées, Vol. 4, 2025</span>
                <div class="btn-group">
                    <a href="#" class="btn">Lire l'article</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">DOI</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="associations">
            <h2>🤝 Engagement Associatif</h2>
            <div class="entry">
                <span class="entry-title">Responsable Communication - Association [Nom]</span>
                <span class="entry-meta">2024 - Présent</span>
                <p>Organisation de colloques et gestion des réseaux sociaux pour promouvoir la recherche.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            &copy; 2026 - [Ton Nom] - Portfolio hébergé sur GitHub
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
